s, property tax increases the overall cost of ownership and affects monthly budgeting, which can influence buying decisions, especially for first-time home buyers.\"\r\n          }\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n          \"@type\": \"Question\",\r\n          \"name\": \"How does property tax affect real estate investors?\",\r\n          \"acceptedAnswer\": {\r\n            \"@type\": \"Answer\",\r\n            \"text\": \"For investors, property tax directly impacts net rental income and return on investment. Higher taxes reduce profitability and must be factored into long-term financial planning.\"\r\n          }\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n          \"@type\": \"Question\",\r\n          \"name\": \"Is property tax the same in every city?\",\r\n          \"acceptedAnswer\": {\r\n            \"@type\": \"Answer\",\r\n            \"text\": \"No, property tax rates and assessment methods vary by city and state depending on local government policies and municipal funding requirements.\"\r\n          }\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n          \"@type\": \"Question\",\r\n          \"name\": \"Can property owners reduce their property tax burden?\",\r\n          \"acceptedAnswer\": {\r\n            \"@type\": \"Answer\",\r\n            \"text\": \"Property owners can reduce tax burden by appealing incorrect assessments, applying for eligible exemptions, and staying informed about local tax policies.\"\r\n          }\r\n        }\r\n      ]\r\n    }\r\n  ]\r\n}\r\n</script>',1,'2026-02-09 06:58:12','2026-02-13 06:33:52',NULL),(61,'noida-vs-gurgaon-real-estate','Noida vs. Gurgaon: Which is the Better Place to Invest in Real Estate?','blog/1771307094_Noida_vs_Gurgaon_jpg','Noida vs Gurgaon','blog/1771307094_Noida_vs_Gurugram_jpg','blog/1771307094_Noida_vs_Gurgaon_jpg','blog/1771307094_Noida_vs_Gurugram_jpg','<p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">When talking about the selection of a location to invest in real estate in the National Capital Region, there are two names that have been taking the front bench for years now: Noida and Gurgaon. Whether you plan on buying a home or investing in property, it becomes very important to know the fine points of difference between the two markets. A debate between real estate investment in Noida and Gurgaon is not only about numbers but also about lifestyle, long-term value, infrastructure, and future potential.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">We, at Great Value Realty, firmly believe that choosing the right destination can turn a purchase into a lifetime asset. This real estate comparison of Noida-Gurgaon helps you look beyond basics and make a strategic choice, whether you are an end user or an investor.</span></p><p><br></p><h2><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">1. Connectivity &amp; Infrastructure</span></h2><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Connectivity is one of the most important factors every buyer should consider before </span><a href=\"https://greatvaluerealty.com/blog/invest-in-noida-real-estate\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);\">investing in real estate in Noida</a><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\"> or Gurgaon.</span></p><p><br></p><h3><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); background-color: transparent;\">Noida</span></h3><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Noida\'s connectivity is one of its best strengths. Noida has several expressways, metro lines, and upcoming projects, such as the Jewar International Airport, indicating that its future is well supported by practicality and connectivity.</span></p><p><br></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Noida Greater Noida</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Upcoming Metro Expansions</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Close access to Delhi and neighbouring commercial hubs</span></li></ul><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Existing and planned infrastructure corridors that enhance accessibility of the NCR region</span></p><p><br></p><h3><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); background-color: transparent;\">Gurgaon</span></h3><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Gurgaon also has good connectivity, particularly to Delhi and the southern NCR. This is through expressways and the metro. However, most of the value relates to corporate nodes and the business environment.</span></p><p><br></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Gurgaon Delhi Expressway</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Rapid metro connectivity</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Proximity to Indira Gandhi International Airport</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Emerging Suburban Growth Corridors</span></li></ul><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Noida vs. Gurgaon real estate investment: The cities are well connected, and Noida\'s larger infrastructure drive makes it a strong contender for investment, especially in the long term.</span></p><p><br></p><h2><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">2. Investment in NCR: Gurgaon vs Noida</span></h2><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">When considering investment in NCR, the Gurgaon vs Noida debate often comes down to balancing corporate-driven demand and premium pricing in Gurgaon with Noida’s expanding infrastructure.</span></p><p><br></p><h3><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); background-color: transparent;\">Noida</span></h3><p><br></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Historically strong price appreciation across key sectors.</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Equivalent demand from families, professionals, and investors</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Sectors 107 and 150 in the high-growth zone are emerging.</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Steady development of infrastructure to support value increase in the future.</span></li></ul><p><br></p><h3><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); background-color: transparent;\">Gurgaon</span></h3><p><br></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Rapid early growth because of the corporate headquarters and multinational presence</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Premium micro‑markets in South and West Gurgaon</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Strong rental demand due to proximity to business parks</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Higher entry prices in certain luxury pockets</span></li></ul><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">A comparison of real estate in Noida and Gurgaon shows that while Noida offers broader opportunities for steady appreciation, Gurgaon excels in corporate-led demand and rental yields in certain zones.</span></p><p><br></p><h2><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">3. Lifestyle &amp; Livability</span></h2><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Lifestyle and livability ultimately depend on whether you prefer Gurgaon’s vibrant, urban pace or Noida’s more spacious, green, and community-focused living environment.</span></p><p><br></p><h3><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); background-color: transparent;\">Noida</span></h3><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">From high-end retail destinations to fine dining, and from expansive parks to family-centric neighbourhoods, Noida has become a world of premium living experiences.</span></p><p><br></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Large townships with community-oriented planning</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Increasing options for entertainment, education, and healthcare</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Well‑planned green spaces and open areas</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Increasing demand for spacious 3 BHK and 4 BHK homes in emerging sectors</span></li></ul><p><br></p><h3><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); background-color: transparent;\">Gurgaon</span></h3><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Gurgaon\'s cosmopolitan vibe attracts professionals seeking a city with premium amenities. The towering luxury high-rises near commercial hubs make it an appealing option for a fast-paced lifestyle.</span></p><p><br></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Premium residential clusters near corporate zones.</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Upscale malls, dining districts, and social hotspots</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Strong emphasis on modern, vertical living</span></li></ul><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">For buyers of homes in either Noida or Gurgaon, the choice largely depends upon one\'s lifestyle preference - a balance of space and community in Noida versus the urbane, fast‑moving environment of Gurgaon.</span></p><p><br></p><h2><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">4. Affordability &amp; Value for Money</span></h2><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Noida generally offers better space and long-term value, while Gurgaon reflects higher pricing due to its corporate-driven premium appeal.</span></p><p><br></p><h3><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); background-color: transparent;\">Noida</span></h3><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Overall, the price level tends to be more competitive than what the Gurgaon sector might offer, particularly for larger residential projects or home types such as expansive 3 and </span><a href=\"https://greatvaluerealty.com/4-bhk-flats-in-noida\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);\">4 BHKs in Noida</a><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">.</span></p><p><br></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Greater range of price points across industries</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Strong resale and rental market due to connectivity</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Value-driven investment opportunities in new sectors</span></li></ul><p><br></p><h3><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); background-color: transparent;\">Gurgaon</span></h3><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Prices in Gurgaon often command a premium due to its corporate nature, particularly in areas near business hubs and luxury shopping districts.</span></p><p><br></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Higher property prices in prime sub-markets</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Strong Rental Demand but Higher Entry Cost</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Premium properties can charge top-tier rents</span></li></ul><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">When Noida or Gurgaon is the location of choice for home buyers, one notices the intrinsic valuation benefits Noida offers to long-term residential investors.</span></p><p><br></p><h2><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">5. Future Growth</span></h2><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Infrastructure growth and commercial expansion will largely determine long-term property appreciation in both Noida and Gurgaon.</span></p><p><br></p><h3><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); background-color: transparent;\">Noida</span></h3><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">The Noida growth story is being written with major infrastructure development and growth plans.</span></p><p><br></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Jewar International Airport is driving regional demand</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Metro expansions are increasing connectivity</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">New commercial and institutional corridors</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Rapid development of mixed-use townships</span></li></ul><p><br></p><h3><span style=\"color: rgb(67, 67, 67); background-color: transparent;\">Gurgaon</span></h3><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Corporate presence and lifestyle hub benefits continue for Gurgaon.</span></p><p><br></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Proximity to prominent business parks</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">High demand for premium office space</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Growth in luxury residential properties in selected industries</span></li></ul><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Noida offers investors seeking the long-term </span><a href=\"https://greatvaluerealty.com/blog/property-tax-real-estate-impact\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);\">effects of property tax changes</a><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\"> and real estate appreciation a variety of growth options.</span></p><p><br></p><h2><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Conclusion: Noida vs Gurgaon — Which to opt for?</span></h2><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">If one is looking for balanced urban living, robust infrastructure growth, and diverse investment opportunities, Noida would be an unbeatable choice. If your interest in real estate lies in proximity to corporations, high-end lifestyle hubs, and high rental yields in select micro-markets, Gurgaon will remain a formidable choice. However, with luxury real estate increasingly changing contours, new sectors in Noida-across well-planned sectors with high-end lifestyle amenities, are now attracting the fancy of a discerning homebuyer and long-term investor.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">At Great Value Realty, we believe in helping buyers find homes that provide not just lifestyle comfort but also sustainable value growth. Whether choosing Noida or Gurgaon, understanding these key differences helps ensure a decision aligned with their goals and positions them for future success.</span></p>','2026-02-17','Noida vs Gurgaon: Which is Better for Real Estate Investment in 2026?','null','Confused between Noida and Gurgaon for property investment? Compare prices, ROI, rental yield, infrastructure, and future growth potential to choose the best real estate destination in NCR.','Great Value Realty','<script type=\"application/ld+json\">\r\n{\r\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\r\n  \"@type\": \"BlogPosting\",\r\n  \"mainEntityOfPage\": {\r\n    \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\r\n    \"@id\": \"https://greatvaluerealty.com/blog/noida-vs-gurgaon-real-estate\"\r\n  },\r\n  \"headline\": \"Noida vs Gurgaon: Which is Better for Real Estate Investment in 2026?\",\r\n  \"description\": \"Confused between Noida and Gurgaon for property investment? Compare prices, ROI, rental yield, infrastructure, and future growth potential to choose the best real estate destination in NCR.\",\r\n  \"image\": \"https://greatvaluerealty.com/gvr-og-img.jpg\",  \r\n  \"author\": {\r\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\r\n    \"name\": \"Great Value Realty\",\r\n    \"url\": \"https://greatvaluerealty.com/\"\r\n  },  \r\n  \"publisher\": {\r\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\r\n    \"name\": \"Great Value Realty\",\r\n    \"logo\": {\r\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\r\n      \"url\": \"https://greatvaluerealty.com/logo.png\" \r\n    }\r\n  },\r\n  \"datePublished\": \"2026-02-17\",\r\n  \"dateModified\": \"2026-02-17\"\r\n}\r\n</script>',1,'2026-02-17 05:44:54','2026-02-23 11:55:18',NULL),(62,'3-bhk-apartment-noida','How to Choose the Perfect 3 BHK Apartment in Noida?','blog/1771841926_3_bhk_apartments_in_noida_jpg','3 bhk apartments in noida','blog/1771841926_3_bhk_apartment_in_noida_jpg','blog/1771841926_3_bhk_apartments_in_noida_jpg','blog/1771841926_3_bhk_apartment_in_noida_jpg','<p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Selecting the right home is one of the most significant decisions you will ever make, especially in a booming real estate market like Noida. Among residential property types, 3 BHK apartments in Noida, just like the Ekanam from Great Value Realty, are the most sought after by families, working professionals, and investors alike, thanks to their optimal balance of size, comfort, and future growth potential. Whether you are looking to buy a 3 BHK in Noida for personal use or investment, this guide will help you make an informed decision by outlining key considerations.</span></p><p><br></p><h2><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">1. Begin with the Right Location</span></h2><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">When you decide to buy a </span><a href=\"https://greatvaluerealty.com/blog/investing-in-3-bhk-flats-sector-107-noida\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);\">3 BHK flat in Sector 107 Noida</a><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">, one of the first things you need to do is select the right location. Noida has many well-connected sectors, each with its own advantages.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Things to keep in mind while selecting a location for your 3 BHK in Noida:</span></p><p><br></p><ul><li><strong style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Connectivity:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\"> Look for a location near metro stations, expressways, and major roads to make travel within the NCR easier.</span></li><li><strong style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Neighbourhood &amp; Infrastructure: </strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">If your location is close to schools, hospitals, markets, and parks, daily life will be easier.</span></li><li><strong style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Development Potential:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\"> If the location is being developed, its value will increase faster.</span></li></ul><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">This way, your 3 BHK in Noida is not only a place to live but also an investment for the future.</span></p><p><br></p><h2><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">2. Know Your Needs in Terms of Space and Lifestyle</span></h2><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Before you shortlist properties, consider how you and your family will utilize the space.</span></p><p><br></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Ask yourself:</strong></p><p><br></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Do you require additional space for a home office or guest room?</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Do you require a bigger living or dining space to suit your lifestyle?</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Will you be living in this property long term, or plan to rent it out in the future?</span></li></ul><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Knowing your space and lifestyle needs will help you shortlist the 3 BHK properties in Noida that suit your needs.</span></p><p><br></p><h2><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">3. Check the Reputation and Quality of Construction by the Builder</span></h2><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">When you are looking to buy a 3 BHK in Noida, the builder\'s reputation and track record are important. A good builder will ensure good construction quality, honesty, and timely delivery of the property.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">What to check:</span></p><p><br></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">The track record of previous projects</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">The quality of construction materials used</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">RERA registration and approvals</span></li></ul><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">A good builder will ensure that when you </span><a href=\"https://greatvaluerealty.com/blog/invest-in-noida-real-estate\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);\">invest in Noida real estate</a><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">, your investment remains safe and your property remains durable.</span></p><p><br></p><h2><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">4. Compare Amenities and Lifestyle Offerings</span></h2><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Today, consumers look for more than just a structure; they look for a better lifestyle. Many 3 BHK apartments in Noida come with attractive amenities.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Typical amenities to look for:</span></p><p><br></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Clubhouse and community hall</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Swimming pool and gym</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Kids play area</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Landscaped gardens and walking paths</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">24x7 security and power backup</span></li></ul><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">These are not only desirable for lifestyle reasons but also increase resale value.</span></p><p><br></p><h2><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">5. Plan Your Budget and Financing Carefully</span></h2><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Purchasing a home requires organising your finances. Before you buy a 3 BHK in Noida, create a budget that covers all potential expenses.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">What to include in the budget:</span></p><p><br></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Cost of the apartment</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Additional costs (parking, club membership, etc.)</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Stamp duty, registration, and other legal charges</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Home loan EMI and interest payments</span></li></ul><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Budgeting for these expenses in advance will ensure smooth execution without financial issues.</span></p><p><br></p><h2><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">6. Inspect the Apartment and Community Thoroughly</span></h2><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Do not purchase an apartment based solely on pictures and advertisements. Always visit the location and inspect the apartment personally.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Important points to check:</span></p><p><br></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Lighting and ventilation</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Quality of fixtures and fittings</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Efficiency of the floor plan</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Noise levels and ambience of the area</span></li></ul><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">A personal inspection will help you determine who will be at the forefront in the </span><a href=\"https://greatvaluerealty.com/blog/noida-vs-gurgaon-real-estate\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);\">Noida vs Gurgaon</a><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\"> race, meeting your requirements.</span></p><p><br></p><h2><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">7. Check Legal Docs and Do Your Due Diligence</span></h2><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Before you finalise your home purchase, ensure that all legal documents are in order.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">The important points to check:</span></p><p><br></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">RERA approval and registration of the project</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Clear land title and possession documents</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Building approvals and no-objection certificates</span></li></ul><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">When you have all your legal documents in place, you are protected from any legal hassles in the future, and you will be completely satisfied with your decision.</span></p><p><br></p><h2><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Conclusion: Decide with Clarity and Confidence</span></h2><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Finding the perfect </span><a href=\"https://greatvaluerealty.com/3-bhk-apartments-noida-expressway\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);\">3 BHK in Noida</a><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\"> requires planning, research, and attention to detail. From choosing the right location and developer, such as Great Value Realty, to considering the facilities and ensuring compliance, every aspect is important when you buy a 3 BHK in Noida. By following this guide, you will make the right decision that suits your lifestyle and investment needs.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Noida is continuously improving its infrastructure and connectivity. Investing in a well-designed 3 BHK will deliver comfort, convenience, and long-term benefits. Developers, prime locations, and amenities that match your lifestyle, because your home should be a place where every moment is special.</span></p>','2026-02-23','How to Choose the Perfect 3 BHK Apartment in Noida?','null','Find best 3 BHK in Noida with our 2026 buyer\'s guide. Compare top sectors, pricing, and essential checklists for a smart real estate investment.','Great Value Realty','<script type=\"application/ld+json\">\r\n{\r\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\r\n  \"@type\": \"BlogPosting\",\r\n  \"mainEntityOfPage\": {\r\n    \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\r\n    \"@id\": \"https://greatvaluerealty.com/blog/3-bhk-apartment-noida\"\r\n  },\r\n  \"headline\": \"How to Choose the Perfect 3 BHK Apartment in Noida?\",\r\n  \"description\": \"Find best 3 BHK in Noida with our 2026 buyer\'s guide. Compare top sectors, pricing, and essential checklists for a smart real estate investment.\",\r\n  \"image\": {\r\n    \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\r\n    \"url\": \"https://greatvaluerealty.com/gvr-og-img.jpg\",\r\n    \"width\": 1200,\r\n    \"height\": 630\r\n  },\r\n  \"author\": {\r\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\r\n    \"name\": \"Great Value Realty\",\r\n    \"url\": \"https://greatvaluerealty.com\"\r\n  },\r\n  \"publisher\": {\r\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\r\n    \"name\": \"Great Value Realty\",\r\n    \"logo\": {\r\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\r\n      \"url\": \"https://greatvaluerealty.com/frontend/images/logos/logo.webp\"\r\n    }\r\n  },\r\n  \"datePublished\": \"2026-02-23T10:00:00+05:30\",\r\n  \"dateModified\": \"2026-02-23T10:00:00+05:30\",\r\n  \"keywords\": \"3 BHK in Noida, luxury apartments Noida, real estate investment Noida 2026, Great Value Sharanam, property buying checklist Noida\"\r\n}\r\n</script>',1,'2026-02-23 10:18:46','2026-02-23 11:54:40',NULL);
