','2025-10-16 05:25:02'),(29,22,'Why should I choose Great Value Realty over other builders in Sector 107 Noida?','With over two decades of experience, Great Value Realty stands out for its customer-centric approach, ethical practices, and high-quality construction. Their Sector 107 projects combine luxury, location, and long-term value.','2025-10-16 05:25:21','2025-10-16 05:25:21'),(30,34,'What features make ready to move flats in Noida sustainable?','These flats often utilise solar power, collect rainwater, feature energy-saving systems, and are constructed with eco-friendly materials.','2025-10-16 05:27:36','2025-10-16 05:27:36'),(31,34,'Why choose Noida for ready to move luxury flats?','Noida is well-connected, boasts modern infrastructure, and features high-quality projects that prioritise sustainable living.','2025-10-16 05:28:35','2025-10-16 05:28:35'),(32,34,'Are sustainable flats more expensive?','Yes, these flats may cost a little more upfront, but you can save money in the long run with lower energy and water bills.','2025-10-16 05:35:11','2025-10-16 05:35:11'),(33,34,'How to verify if a project is truly sustainable?','Look for IGBC or GRIHA certifications, and verify if the project features include solar panels, water recycling, and green areas.','2025-10-16 05:35:24','2025-10-16 05:35:24'),(34,34,'What are the benefits of ready-to-move luxury flats?','You can move in right away, avoid waiting, and see all the sustainable features for yourself before making a purchase.','2025-10-16 05:35:34','2025-10-16 05:35:34'),(35,33,'What flat configurations are available at Anandam Noida for first-time homebuyers?','Anandam offers spacious 2 & 3 BHK ready to move flats in Noida, ideal for modern families.','2025-10-16 06:05:05','2025-10-16 06:05:05'),(36,33,'Where is Anandam located and how good is the connectivity?','Located in Sector-107 Noida, Anandam provides excellent connectivity via Noida Expressway, Yamuna Expressway, and metro access.','2025-10-16 06:05:19','2025-10-16 06:05:19'),(37,33,'What are the key amenities at Anandam?','Residents enjoy a clubhouse, swimming pool, gym, landscaped gardens, kids’ play zones, and 24/7 security.','2025-10-16 06:05:32','2025-10-16 06:05:32'),(38,33,'Is Great Value Anandam a family-friendly community?','Absolutely! Great Value Anandam is designed with families in mind, featuring spacious homes, safety measures, and a community-oriented atmosphere.','2025-10-16 06:05:46','2026-01-13 07:05:40'),(39,33,'What specifications and special features set Anandam apart for first-time buyers?','All-corner flats, only 4 units per floor, double-height lobby, cross ventilation, and premium finishes make Anandam unique.','2025-10-16 06:05:58','2025-10-16 06:05:58'),(40,39,'What makes Sector 107, Noida ideal for 4 BHK flat investment?','Sector 107 offers premium infrastructure, proximity to commercial hubs, metro connectivity, and modern amenities, making it a highly sought-after location for 4 BHK flats.','2025-10-16 06:11:12','2025-10-16 06:11:12'),(41,39,'Are 4 BHK flats in Sector 107 suitable for families?','Yes, 4 BHK flats provide ample space, privacy, and luxury features, making them perfect for families seeking comfort and convenience in Noida.','2025-10-16 06:11:26','2025-10-16 06:11:26'),(42,39,'How is the connectivity of Sector 107, Noida?','Sector 107 is well-connected via NH-24, Noida-Greater Noida Expressway, and the metro, ensuring easy access to Delhi, Noida, and nearby commercial and educational hubs.','2025-10-16 06:11:43','2025-10-16 06:11:43'),(43,39,'What amenities are expected in 4 BHK flats in Sector 107?','Most premium projects offer landscaped gardens, swimming pools, clubhouses, gyms, 24/7 security, dedicated parking, and children’s play areas.','2025-10-16 06:11:58','2025-10-16 06:11:58'),(44,39,'Is investing in 4 BHK flats in Sector 107 profitable?','Yes, the region is witnessing high demand due to upcoming infrastructure projects, making it a lucrative option for long-term capital appreciation.','2025-10-16 06:12:10','2025-10-16 06:12:10'),(45,38,'What are the top new residential properties in Sector 107, Noida?','Some of the top new residential properties in Sector 107, Noida include luxurious 2 BHK, 3 BHK, and 4 BHK apartments offering modern amenities, strategic location, and excellent connectivity to major hubs in Noida and Delhi.','2025-10-16 06:13:39','2025-10-16 06:13:39'),(46,38,'Why should I invest in residential properties in Sector 107, Noida?','Sector 107 offers a rapidly developing infrastructure, well-connected roadways, close proximity to commercial areas, and high appreciation potential, making it an attractive investment destination.','2025-10-16 06:13:53','2025-10-16 06:13:53'),(47,38,'What amenities are available in new residential properties in Sector 107?','New residential properties in Sector 107 offer premium amenities like swimming pools, gyms, clubhouses, landscaped gardens, children\'s play areas, 24/7 security, and ample parking space.','2025-10-16 06:14:11','2025-10-16 06:14:11'),(48,38,'How is the connectivity in Sector 107 for residents?','Sector 107 is strategically connected via NH-24, the Noida-Greater Noida Expressway, and the upcoming metro line, offering easy access to major commercial, educational, and healthcare hubs in Noida and Delhi.','2025-10-16 06:14:25','2025-10-16 06:14:25'),(49,37,'Why should I consider investing in a luxury home in Noida?','Because Noida is growing fast, with strong infrastructure, high demand from professionals, and the potential for good capital appreciation.','2025-10-16 06:17:31','2025-10-16 06:17:31'),(50,37,'What benefits do luxury homes offer over regular residences?','Better amenities, higher build quality, premium locations, and more comfort — which also attract better long-term returns.','2025-10-16 06:17:45','2025-10-16 06:17:45'),(51,37,'What kind of rental yield can one expect from a luxury property in Noida?','Luxury homes often command higher rents due to the features and location, so yields tend to be above average compared to standard apartments.','2025-10-16 06:18:02','2025-10-16 06:18:02'),(52,37,'How is Noida’s infrastructure development supporting luxury real estate?','Improved connectivity (roads, metro), planned townships, and better urban amenities make luxury properties more desirable and accessible.','2025-10-16 06:18:14','2025-10-16 06:18:14'),(53,37,'Are luxury homes in Noida a safe investment in terms of regulatory compliance?','Yes, reputable projects usually require approvals (RERA, building permissions, etc.), which help reduce risk.','2025-10-16 06:18:30','2025-10-16 06:18:30'),(54,36,'What is the carpet area under RERA?','Carpet area is the usable floor space inside the walls of an apartment, excluding balconies, terraces, and common areas.','2025-10-16 06:21:19','2025-10-16 06:21:19'),(55,36,'Why is carpet area important?','It shows the actual livable space you get, ensuring transparent pricing.','2025-10-16 06:21:36','2025-10-16 06:21:36'),(56,36,'How is carpet area calculated?','By adding the internal room areas, excluding walls, ducts, balconies, and shafts.','2025-10-16 06:21:55','2025-10-16 06:21:55'),(57,36,'Can builders charge on built-up area?','No, RERA mandates pricing only on carpet area.','2025-10-16 06:22:08','2025-10-16 06:22:08'),(58,36,'Are balconies included in the carpet area?','No, balconies, verandahs, and terraces are excluded.','2025-10-16 06:22:21','2025-10-16 06:22:21'),(59,35,'What types of luxury apartments are available in Sector 107, Noida?','You can find premium 3 BHK and 4 BHK apartments with modern amenities.','2025-10-16 06:27:16','2025-10-16 06:27:16'),(60,35,'Are there ready-to-move flats in Sector 107, Noida?','Yes, several 3 BHK and 4 BHK ready-to-move options are available.','2025-10-16 06:27:29','2025-10-16 06:27:29'),(61,35,'What amenities do luxury apartments in Sector 107 offer?','Gated security, clubhouse, gym, pool, landscaped gardens, and parking.','2025-10-16 06:27:43','2025-10-16 06:27:43'),(62,35,'What is the price range of these apartments?','Prices vary by size, location, and amenities. Contact Great Value Realty for details.','2025-10-16 06:27:57','2025-10-16 06:27:57'),(63,35,'Is RERA registration important for these projects?','Yes, always check RERA registration for safety and transparency.','2025-10-16 06:28:09','2025-10-16 06:28:09'),(69,31,'Why invest in apartments in Noida Sector 107?','This sector offers premium infrastructure, excellent connectivity, and high potential for long-term property appreciation.','2025-10-16 06:45:02','2025-10-16 06:45:02'),(70,31,'What are the benefits of living in high-rise apartments in Sector 107?','Residents enjoy modern amenities, panoramic views, enhanced security, elevators, and a self-contained community lifestyle.','2025-10-16 06:45:16','2025-10-16 06:45:16'),(71,31,'What types of apartments are available in Sector 107, Noida?','Sector 107 offers 2 BHK, 3 BHK, and 4 BHK high-rise apartments with contemporary designs and spacious layouts.','2025-10-16 06:45:30','2025-10-16 06:45:30'),(72,31,'Are high-rise apartments in Sector 107 safe for families?','Yes, these apartments include fire safety systems, secure access, parking facilities, and other safety measures for family living.','2025-10-16 06:45:43','2025-10-16 06:45:43'),(73,31,'What factors should buyers consider before investing in Sector 107 apartments?','Consider location, builder reputation, legal approvals, cost, and potential rental yield before investing.','2025-10-16 06:45:55','2025-10-16 06:45:55'),(74,30,'What is an Occupancy Certificate (OC)?','An OC is a legal document certifying that a building is constructed as per approved plans and is fit for occupation.','2025-10-16 06:56:25','2025-10-16 06:56:25'),(75,30,'Why is an OC important for buyers?','It ensures the property is legal, safe, and free from future legal issues','2025-10-16 06:56:41','2025-10-16 06:56:41'),(76,30,'Can a property be occupied without an OC?','No, occupying without an OC is illegal and may lead to fines or demolition.','2025-10-16 06:56:54','2025-10-16 06:56:54'),(77,30,'How to verify an OC?','Check with the local municipal authority or development body to confirm its authenticity.','2025-10-16 06:57:05','2025-10-16 06:57:05'),(78,30,'What happens if a property doesn’t have an OC?','It may cause legal issues, difficulties in resale, and problems securing loans.','2025-10-16 06:57:23','2025-10-16 06:57:23'),(79,29,'What makes Great Value Sharanam special?','Great Value Sharanam combines modern architecture, thoughtful layouts, and premium amenities, offering a unique living experience in Noida.','2025-10-16 07:43:59','2025-10-16 07:43:59'),(80,29,'Are there luxury apartments in Sector 107 Noida at Sharanam?','Yes, Sharanam offers luxury apartments in Sector 107 Noida with spacious designs, high-end finishes, and landscaped surroundings.','2025-10-16 07:44:21','2025-10-16 07:44:21'),(81,29,'What types of apartments are available at Sharanam?','The project offers 3 BHK and 4 BHK apartments designed for comfort, privacy, and modern urban living.','2025-10-16 07:44:34','2025-10-16 07:44:34'),(82,29,'What amenities are available at Great Value Sharanam?','Amenities include landscaped gardens, clubhouse, swimming pool, 24/7 security, and dedicated parking.','2025-10-16 07:44:49','2025-10-16 07:44:49'),(83,29,'Where is Great Value Sharanam located?','Sharanam is located in Sector 107, Noida, providing excellent connectivity to Noida Expressway, Delhi NCR, schools, hospitals, and shopping centers.','2025-10-16 07:45:01','2025-10-16 07:45:01'),(84,28,'Why is Noida ideal for commercial investment now?','Noida offers strong infrastructure, metro access, and rising demand from IT and retail sectors.','2025-10-16 07:48:28','2025-10-16 07:48:28'),(85,28,'What types of commercial properties are available?','Options include office spaces, retail shops, food courts, showrooms, and co-working hubs.','2025-10-16 07:48:44','2025-10-16 07:48:44'),(86,28,'What are the benefits of commercial investment in Noida?','High rental yields, capital appreciation, and proximity to Delhi make it a lucrative market.','2025-10-16 07:48:57','2026-01-13 07:09:40'),(87,28,'Why now a good time to invest in commercial properties in Noida?','With upcoming projects and growing demand, now is a promising time for commercial investment.','2025-10-16 07:49:19','2026-01-13 07:09:19'),(93,26,'What types of flats are available at Eternia Residences?','Eternia offers spacious 3 BHK, 3 BHK + Study, and 4 BHK apartments.','2025-10-17 06:06:20','2025-10-17 06:06:20'),(94,26,'Where is Eternia located?','It is located in Tech Zone IV, Greater Noida West, with excellent connectivity to Delhi, Noida, metro stations, schools, and hospitals.','2025-10-17 06:06:43','2025-10-17 06:06:43'),(95,26,'What amenities does the project offer?','Amenities include a clubhouse, gym, swimming pool, landscaped gardens, kids’ play area, jogging track, and EV charging points.','2025-10-17 06:07:02','2025-10-17 06:07:02'),(96,26,'Why invest in Eternia Residences?','It offers prime location, strong appreciation potential, spacious layouts, and the credibility of NBCC and Great Value Realty.','2025-10-17 06:07:21','2025-10-17 06:07:21'),(97,26,'When is the possession expected?','The project is under development, with possession timelines as per the builder’s construction schedule.','2025-10-17 06:07:54','2025-10-17 06:07:54'),(98,25,'What does BHK mean in real estate?','BHK stands for Bedroom, Hall, Kitchen. For example, 2 BHK = 2 bedrooms, 1 hall, 1 kitchen.','2025-10-17 06:26:59','2025-10-17 06:26:59'),(99,25,'What is the difference between 1 BHK, 2 BHK, 3 BHK flats?','1 BHK suits singles/couples, 2 BHK is ideal for small families, and 3 BHK is best for medium to large families.','2025-10-17 06:27:23','2025-10-17 06:27:23'),(100,25,'How does BHK affect the price of a flat?','More bedrooms mean larger area and higher cost. Location and amenities also influence price.','2025-10-17 06:27:38','2025-10-17 06:27:38'),(101,25,'Is a 1 BHK enough for a family?','It can work for small families, but 2 BHK or 3 BHK offers more comfort and space.','2025-10-17 06:27:51','2025-10-17 06:27:51'),(102,25,'How to choose the right BHK?','Consider your family size, budget, location, lifestyle, and future needs.','2025-10-17 06:28:06','2025-10-17 06:28:06'),(103,24,'What configurations of apartments are available at Anandam?','Great Value Anandam offers 2, 3 and 4 BHK units designed to suit different family sizes','2025-10-17 06:36:36','2025-10-17 06:36:36'),(104,24,'What key amenities does Anandam provide that appeal to families?','The project includes features like landscaped green spaces, clubhouse, swimming pool, and 24/7 security.','2025-10-17 06:36:51','2025-10-17 06:36:51'),(105,24,'How is the connectivity from Anandam to essential services?','Anandam is strategically located in Sector 107, Noida with easy access to schools, hospitals, shopping areas, and major roads/expressways.','2025-10-17 06:37:03','2025-10-17 06:37:03'),(106,24,'Who is the developer behind Anandam, and is it a trustworthy brand?','The project is by Great Value Realty / Great Value Projects India, a developer known for delivering quality residential projects in Noida','2025-10-17 06:37:17','2025-10-17 06:37:17'),(107,24,'What makes Anandam especially suitable for families rather than bachelors or investors?','Its thoughtfully designed layouts, family-friendly amenities, secure environment, and proximity to schools and essential infrastructure make it ideal for family living.','2025-10-17 06:37:31','2025-10-17 06:37:31'),(108,23,'What is FSI in real estate?','FSI (Floor Space Index) or FAR (Floor Area Ratio) defines how much floor area can be built on a particular plot of land. It helps regulate building height, density, and construction limits as per government norms.','2025-10-17 06:44:19','2025-10-17 06:44:19'),(109,23,'How is FSI calculated?','FSI is calculated using the formula — FSI = Total Built-up Area ÷ Plot Area. For example, if a plot measures 1,000 sq. m and the FSI is 2, you can construct up to 2,000 sq. m of total floor area.','2025-10-17 06:50:31','2025-10-17 06:50:31'),(110,23,'Why is FSI important in real estate development?','FSI determines how much space a developer can use, directly affecting project design, cost, and pricing. It ensures proper land use, maintains city planning balance, and prevents overcrowding.','2025-10-17 06:50:42','2025-10-17 06:50:42'),(111,23,'What factors influence the FSI of a property?','The approved FSI depends on several factors like location, type of zone (residential or commercial), road width, available infrastructure, and local building regulations set by development authorities.','2025-10-17 06:50:52','2025-10-17 06:50:52'),(112,23,'What are the benefits of a higher FSI?','A higher FSI allows developers to build more floors, utilize land efficiently, and provide better amenities. It also increases property value and housing availability in urban areas.','2025-10-17 06:51:22','2025-10-17 06:51:22'),(113,15,'Is RERA registration mandatory for properties in Noida?','Yes, always check if the project is RERA-registered. It ensures transparency and protects buyers’ rights.','2025-10-17 06:54:37','2025-10-17 06:54:37'),(114,15,'How much extra should I budget apart from the property price?','You should keep aside 10–15% extra for stamp duty, registration, maintenance, parking, and other charges.','2025-10-17 06:54:51','2025-10-17 06:54:51'),(115,15,'How do I check a developer’s credibility?','Research online reviews, visit past projects, and verify delivery timelines before investing.','2025-10-17 06:55:03','2025-10-17 06:55:03'),(116,15,'Can I rely only on online property listings?','No. Always conduct physical site visits to confirm infrastructure, finishing quality, and locality convenience.','2025-10-17 06:55:15','2025-10-17 06:55:15'),(11